abstract_ssm: The Carole De Saram papers include materials gathered and produced by De Saram as a result of her involvement in Tribeca community affairs. De Saram is both the former Chair of Community Board 1 in Manhattan and the former President of the Tribeca Community Association. The bulk of the content is textual with some photographs, maps, and ephemera included.
